description:
What is the true origin of the Ten Commandments, and how do they reflect God's eternal character of love?

Discover the profound depth behind the moment Moses received the Ten Commandments on Mount Sinai, written by God's hand. Learn how these commandments serve as more than just rules; they manifest God's love, existing since eternity. 

To watch the full video from Elder Ted Wilson, president of the General Conference of Seventh-day Adventists, paste this link into your browser:
https://youtu.be/53Ao3DcwfmA
